<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. ثُمَّ اقْتَضَى أَمْرًا وَنَهْيًا عَلَّهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَتَمَيَّزُ التَّقْوَى عَنِ الْعِصْيَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَوُلِدْتَ مَفْطُورًا بِفِطْرَتِكَ الَّتِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَيْسَتْ سِوَى التَّصْدِيقِ وَالإيمَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَبُلِيتَ بِالتَّكْلِيفِ أَنْتَ مُخَيَّرٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَمَامَكَ النَّجْدَانِ مُفْتَتَحَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَعَمِلْتَ مَا تَهْوَى وَأَنْتَ مُرَاقَبٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَا كُنْتَ مَحْجُوبًا عَنِ الدَّيَّانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ثُمَّ انْقَضَى الْعُمْرُ الَّذِي تَهْنَا بِهِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَبَدَأْتَ فِي ضَعْفٍ وَفِي نُقْصَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَدَنَا الْفِرَاقُ وَلاتَ حِينَ تَهَرُّبٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَيْنَ الْمَفَرُّ مِن الْقَضَاءِ الدَّانِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالْتَفَّ صَحْبُكَ يَرْقُبُونَ بِحَسْرَةٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَاذَا تَكُونُ عَوَاقِبُ الْحَدَثَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَاسْتَلَّ رُوحَكَ وَالْقُلُوبُ تَقَطَّعَتْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>حَزَنًا وَأَلْقَتْ دَمْعَهَا الْعَيْنَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَاجْتَاحَ أَهْلَ الدَّارِ حُزْنٌ بَالِغٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَاجْتَاحَ مَنْ حَضَرُوا مِنَ الْجِيرَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَالْبِنْتُ عَبْرَى لِلْفِرَاقِ كَئِيبَةً<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَالدَّمْعُ يَمْلأ سَاحَةَ الأَجْفَانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَالزَّوْجَ ثَكْلَى وَالصِّغَارُ تَجَمَّعُوا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>يَتَطَّلَعُونَ تَطَلُّعَ الْحَيْرَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>